For generating certificate
-----------------------------
keytool -genkey -keyalg RSA -alias localhost -keystore C:\Users\mkumar\Downloads\market-scan.jks -storepass shraddha@6mar -validity 360 -keysize 2048

eneable ssl connector in tomact\server.xml
-------------------------------------------
<Connector SSLEnabled="true" keystoreFile="C:/Users/manish2aug/market-scan.keystore" keystorePass="shraddha@6mar" port="8443" scheme="https" secure="true" sslProtocol="TLS"/>